{"tid":2281591,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"丹麥倡議　發現原來用左數千零萬，眾籌的錢　可以用上餘生來量度","createTime":"2020-11-11T09:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T09:28:55.000Z","uid":38189,"like":34,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d0095ded7d0bff25780f7af6b92d0215e7c47d6e","tid":2281591,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T09:32:13.000Z","msg":"攬炒完害怕的你一轉臉<br />\n用運動收到了幾多金錢<br />\n當我工作睡覺禱告娛樂那麼刻意賺錢課金<br />\n誰料你竟偷走了沒有見面<br />\n<br />\n誰當初肯捐獻看迪仔交代<br />\n過後誰人說投訴左螞蟻集團<br />\n直到捐錢過後才知獻金已斷送<br />\n返英國然後上報紙仍然在賺錢<br />\n<br />\n丹麥倡議　發現原來用左數千零萬<br />\n眾籌的錢　可以用上餘生來量度<br />\n但佢都未搵夠　靠著沿途黃絲的送贈<br />\n能著草到英國　或是其實再走去德國<br />\n然後美國攬炒會受益中國<br />\n無奈被你呃過錢 沒回報<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b4bf361ba545da277c60295546d1e2242eced5","tid":2281591,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T09:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46e107c0b320d479d6dcb054a26f7113bd6318d","tid":2281591,"uid":261505,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T09:33:33.000Z","msg":"更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEc0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=16192318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網"},{"pid":"04e2fee8505284ec3956caf706fc25dbb15b883b","tid":2281591,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T09:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7283c1124e85cc282f1b8a792fe5e341563d0691","tid":2281591,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T09:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\"